# THE BOUNDARY (PROTOCOL section 15): paths goose may not touch, on top
# of the built-in floor (.env*, *.pem, *.key, credentials*, ~/.ssh,
# ~/.aws, ~/.gnupg, ...). One pattern per line: a bare name or glob
# masks matching basenames anywhere; a pattern with / is an anchored
# path masked whole. No ! negation.
#
# This file's PRESENCE also upgrades "bubblewrap missing" from a nudge
# to a refusal (exit 4): commit it and nobody runs unsandboxed by
# accident.
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3